</div>--><p><img src="assets/photos/Yeast-robot.jpg" alt="Yeast robot" width="190" height="253" />CISBAN's aim is to advance understanding of the complex mechanisms underpinning the ageing process and of how          these are affected by nutrition, through the field of research known as systems biology.</p>
